<% if @game.draw? %>

<%= @game.players[0].name %> chose <%= @game.results[:player1] %>!
<%= @game.players[1].name %> also chose <%= @game.results[:player2] %>!

It was a draw.

<% else %>

<%= @game.players[0].name %> chose <%= @game.results[:player1] %>!
<%= @game.players[1].name %> chose <%= @game.results[:player2] %>!

<%= @game.winner.name %> is the winner!

<% end %>

